{"tid":1749872,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［告急］票站要人","createTime":"2019-11-24T07:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T07:14:46.000Z","uid":26071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c9c351585a00a9bb7273d0845494fb4dfd3dc0","tid":1749872,"uid":26071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:14:46.000Z","msg":"唔好以為投票率高就贏<br />\n純粹係對家動員能力高咋<br />\n<br />\n望吓今日投票率由頭帶到依家嘅九龍城區<br />\n24個議員入面有20個係建制<br />\n有李慧琼紮根嘅土瓜灣北 仲有啟晴德朗兩條紅邨<br />\n擺明係對家出盡力催票<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b6nZbMH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb6nZbMH.png&h=b9c91643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家快d出黎投票呀<br />\n到時真係高投票率輸選戰 國際戰線就打唔響<br />\n香港正式變新疆</span>"}]}